    {
      "id": "product-project-overview",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Product / Project Nodeset",
      "position": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": -430
      },
      "width": 500,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Product / Project Nodeset\n\nCandidate types from the source board:\n- `initiative`\n- `feature`\n- `problem`\n- `user-need`\n- `decision`\n- `constraint`\n- `release`\n- `metric`\n- `risk`\n- `open-question`\n\nThis family is close to planning, but aimed at product semantics and delivery framing rather than generic work management.\n\nThis graph now also includes a bounded agent-prompting slice so you can see how the new nodeset behaves inside a normal task graph.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
