    {
      "id": "product-project-dependency-note",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Product Relationships",
      "position": {
        "x": 1080,
        "y": 320
      },
      "width": 500,
      "height": 420,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Product Relationships\n\nLikely typed edges:\n- `feature` solves `problem`\n- `feature` serves `user-need`\n- `initiative` groups `feature`\n- `metric` measures `feature` or `initiative`\n\nImplementation pressure:\n- product graphs should roll into planning graphs\n- release/version logic may need separate substrate work\n- metric summaries should support portfolio-level views\n\nStatus:\n- package root created\n- template created\n- class artifacts created\n- planning reuse remains explicit",
